I'm not sure what the owner does to the boba but it's the best boba place I've ever been to in AZ. The boba tastes sweet and the drinks themselves are made very well. The owner doesn't just hire anyone and makes sure the quality of the drinks remain consistent. My favorite flavor is the chocolate banana smoothie with boba. A must try! Also, if you want to combine flavors, she (the owner) will definitely let you.

